  "title": "Senior Quantity Surveyor (LTA Projects) #80622",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Construction</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Senior Quantity Surveyor</strong></li><li>Working Location: Jurong West</li><li>Working Hours: 5 Days, Monday – Friday (8am – 5.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage cost-related matters for construction projects, from initial cost estimates to final settlement of accounts.</li><li>Prepare, review, and negotiate contracts, cost variations, and related claims.</li><li>Provide ongoing cost control support and financial advice throughout all stages of the project.</li><li>Coordinate and communicate with project managers, site teams, clients, and subcontractors.</li><li>Ensure work complies with contract terms, company procedures, and relevant industry standards.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma in Quantity Surveying, Building, or a related field.</li><li>At least 5 years of relevant experience in construction projects, preferably dealing with LTA projects.</li><li>Good understanding of construction contracts, including measurement and valuation.</li><li>Strong negotiation, communication, and analytical skills.</li><li>Proficient in MS Office and relevant quantity surveying software.</li><li>Proficient in AutoCAD software for basic drafting and design-related tasks.</li><li>Able to work independently and collaborate effectively in a team.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80622 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
